{"tid":108401,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"AMD AM4 平台仍表態支援 Windows 7","createTime":"2017-02-05T08:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T12:42:58.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6dca5bd207e4f70117697a2e41456db6353f8620","tid":108401,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T08:33:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.coolaler.com/threads/amd-am4-%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E4%BB%8D%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4-windows-7.342089/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com%2Fthreads%2Famd-am4-%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%258F%25B0%25E4%25BB%258D%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2585%258B%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258F%25B4-windows-7.342089%2F&d=Ru8OiKpQtXbNv5YRwinC6gRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=cae06019\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.coolaler.com/threads/amd-am4-%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E4%BB%8D%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4-windows-7.342089/</a><br />\n<br />\nIntel 在這一代 Kaby Lake 處理器以及200系列平台上明確表態放棄支援 Windows 7，不過各廠商還沒那麼快放棄，畢竟還得考慮到使用者涵蓋率，Windows 7 的用戶還不算少，不支援就是跟業績過不去，所以上面即便不支援，但各主板廠商還是有相關驅動可以下載使用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.coolaler.com.tw/image/news/17/02/am4_pf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com.tw%2Fimage%2Fnews%2F17%2F02%2Fam4_pf.jpg&h=cbe7ae75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n那麼即將上市的 AMD AM4 呢？據消息稱 AMD 仍表態將會提供 Windows 7 系統的支援，包括第七代 APU Bristol Bidge 的內顯驅動，以及三款 AM4 平台主板晶片組 X370、B350 和 A320 的驅動程式，畢竟 AMD 處理器在這幾年中高階這塊多處於劣勢，大家滿心期待的 Ryzen 當然能迎合大眾口味最好。"},{"pid":"f1b9327178adb78107b1d66393bfc4e9b4d8ca44","tid":108401,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T08:49:35.000Z","msg":"似乎係要挽留用AMD 平台嘅公司客戶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400fb8c765d853e4454445f7f6ce469694555782","tid":108401,"uid":64401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:45:38.000Z","msg":"等到頸都長埋，快D出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid